1
00:00:02,887 --> 00:00:07,899
ظآزDo you know, our fingertips
are bound by one stringظآز

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:12,499
ظآزTied to an attachment
that blooms only to fadeظآز

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,999
ظآزBy your side onceظآز

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,074
ظآزI laughed with the world
wild and freeظآز

5
00:00:17,075 --> 00:00:21,049
ظآزYet now there's no one
to carry the story onظآز

6
00:00:21,050 --> 00:00:25,970
ظآزDo you know you are the one string
woven through my fateظآز

7
00:00:25,987 --> 00:00:30,699
ظآزCoiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's lineظآز

8
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:35,261
ظآزIf love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flightظآز

9
00:00:35,262 --> 00:00:40,445
ظآزYet I still came to answer your callظآز

10
00:00:40,725 --> 00:00:43,157
=Shall We Dance=

11
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:46,132
=Episode 11=

12
00:00:57,260 --> 00:00:58,380
I ran out of ink.

13
00:01:16,820 --> 00:01:18,020
Are you alright?

14
00:01:22,980 --> 00:01:24,100
I'm fine.

15
00:02:04,060 --> 00:02:05,139
(This won't do.)

16
00:02:05,140 --> 00:02:06,460
(We must talk it through.)

17
00:02:08,100 --> 00:02:09,220
Xiao Man.

18
00:02:10,820 --> 00:02:11,659
Xiao Man.

19
00:02:11,660 --> 00:02:12,900
I want some water.

20
00:02:15,140 --> 00:02:16,260
Xiao Man.

21
00:02:16,420 --> 00:02:17,660
I want some water.

22
00:03:15,540 --> 00:03:16,660
Xiao Man...

23
00:03:16,780 --> 00:03:17,900
You...

24
00:03:20,420 --> 00:03:21,540
I...

25
00:04:11,620 --> 00:04:13,660
(Why is her face so pale?)

26
00:04:15,020 --> 00:04:16,140
(No.)

27
00:04:16,340 --> 00:04:17,620
(I must check on her.)

28
00:04:26,100 --> 00:04:27,220
Xiao Man.

29
00:04:34,740 --> 00:04:35,860
Xiao Man.

30
00:04:41,980 --> 00:04:43,099
You're burning up.

31
00:04:43,100 --> 00:04:44,300
You have a fever.

32
00:04:53,660 --> 00:04:55,579
Does Your Majesty want water again?

33
00:04:55,580 --> 00:04:56,459
No.

34
00:04:56,460 --> 00:04:59,020
I didn't know you were hurt this badly.
Let me see.

35
00:05:04,660 --> 00:05:05,780
Blood...

36
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:07,380
You're coughing up blood.

37
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:09,779
Someone!

38
00:05:09,780 --> 00:05:10,900
Someone, help!

39
00:05:11,020 --> 00:05:11,940
Xiao Man!

40
00:05:12,180 --> 00:05:13,460
Someone, help!

41
00:05:31,020 --> 00:05:32,140
Your Majesty,

42
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:34,420
this sudden illness

43
00:05:34,980 --> 00:05:36,900
will trouble him for a few days.

44
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:38,260
However,

45
00:05:38,300 --> 00:05:39,619
he'll recover soon

46
00:05:39,620 --> 00:05:41,420
so long as he takes
his medicine on time.

47
00:05:41,860 --> 00:05:43,420
There's no need to worry.

48
00:05:43,820 --> 00:05:44,940
Understood.

49
00:05:45,260 --> 00:05:46,380
Then...

50
00:05:46,460 --> 00:05:48,140
I will take my leave.

51
00:05:48,620 --> 00:05:49,940
Thank you.

52
00:06:12,820 --> 00:06:14,660
We should summon the Imperial Physician.

53
00:06:15,180 --> 00:06:16,259
Never mind.

54
00:06:16,260 --> 00:06:18,140
He's already examined me.

55
00:06:22,100 --> 00:06:23,460
Don't blame yourself.

56
00:06:23,740 --> 00:06:25,140
It wasn't because of you.

57
00:06:27,580 --> 00:06:29,060
After one night's rest,

58
00:06:29,420 --> 00:06:31,020
I'll be fine.

59
00:06:31,780 --> 00:06:32,980
It's nothing.

60
00:06:35,500 --> 00:06:36,620
Take your medicine.

61
00:07:10,340 --> 00:07:11,460
Xiao Man...

62
00:07:13,940 --> 00:07:15,740
I didn't mean it.

63
00:07:16,125 --> 00:07:18,205
I didn't know you'd be standing there.

64
00:07:20,140 --> 00:07:21,740
It had nothing to do with you.

65
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:26,180
I'd like to rest now.

66
00:08:31,725 --> 00:08:32,845
Xiao Man...

67
00:08:34,380 --> 00:08:37,260
I thought after you returned,
we'd be just like we were as children.

68
00:08:39,060 --> 00:08:40,940
Why is this happening?

69
00:08:45,660 --> 00:08:46,820
Why?

70
00:09:10,587 --> 00:09:14,507
ظآزI wanted to ask you
the meaning of foreverظآز

71
00:09:14,912 --> 00:09:18,032
ظآزIs it longing that never restsظآز

72
00:09:18,687 --> 00:09:21,944
ظآزLove that echoes without endظآز

73
00:09:23,237 --> 00:09:26,832
ظآزOr promises that can't be keptظآز

74
00:09:28,787 --> 00:09:32,207
ظآزAll those vows of forever we madeظآز

75
00:09:32,749 --> 00:09:36,194
ظآزAre sealed away in darkness nowظآز

76
00:09:37,987 --> 00:09:40,794
ظآزHow cruelظآز

77
00:09:40,912 --> 00:09:45,069
ظآزLove blooms and withersظآز

78
00:09:47,262 --> 00:09:51,344
ظآزThe more I try to forget
the fiercer the love burnsظآز

79
00:09:51,637 --> 00:09:55,732
ظآزThe more I retreat
the sharper it feelsظآز

80
00:09:56,099 --> 00:09:59,411
ظآزHow am I supposed to let goظآز

81
00:09:59,412 --> 00:10:03,494
ظآزAnd bring this story to an endظآز

82
00:10:05,375 --> 00:10:08,982
ظآزAfter ten thousand years
adrift in the mortal worldظآز

83
00:10:09,375 --> 00:10:13,520
ظآزWhy is my wish still unfulfilledظآز

84
00:10:13,587 --> 00:10:22,249
ظآزHow absurd
that this longing just won't dieظآز

